USAGE:

    <actAction type="$ACTION_TYPE"
           (o) wait="$TIME"
           (o) actor="$ACTOR"
               - actorRef="$ACTOR_REFERENCE"
    />


    (o)                 - Optional attribute
        -               - Must be included if you use THAT optional attribute

    $ACTION_TYPE        - The action to act by the actor
    $TIME               - true or false, whether or not to wait for the action to be
                          performed completely before proceeding to the next command.

    $ACTOR              - The actor to perform this action.
                          For details, read on 'actor_references.txt'

    $ACTOR_REFERENCE    - The actor you want to refer to
